 gloves, including black and yellow, cut an sewn nitrile, cut, heat, and impact resistant, Canadian, cryogenic, driver, knitted, latex, leather, mechanical, nitrile, PU, seamless and sustainable nitrile, thermal, and welder gloves, as well as leather accessories. It also provides disposable, denim, flame retardant, heavy, hi vis, light, multinorm, occupational, rainwear, soft shell and polo, sustainable, thermal, and women's workwear; and safety shoes. The company serves aerospace and aviation, automobile and auto ancillary, agriculture, electronics and IT, biotechnology, glass and ceramic, chem,ical and paint, infrastructure, healthcare, defense and security, Horeca, logistics and transporation, manufacturing, metal and mining, pharmaceuticals, and oil and gas industries. It also exports its products. Mallcom (India) Limited was incorporated in 1983 and is headquartered in Kolkata, India."}}